title: Nothing in these provisions shall restrain the C
clause_text: Nothing in these provisions shall restrain the C.E.O. from issuing of orders for preparation of the eligibility list (Annexure II) in relation to any Slum declared u/s 4 of the Slum Act or Slum Rehabilitation Area declared u/s 3-C of the said Act, wherein a proposal is submitted or not. Thus the fixing of eligibility (Annexure II) will be independent of any scheme submitted.
